    <briefdescription>
<para>Information about the termination of a periodic advertising sync. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct provides information about the termination of a periodic advertising sync. It includes the advertiser’s address and SID, along with the reason for the sync termination. This information is provided in the callback when the sync is terminated, either due to a local or remote request, or due to missing data (e.g., out of range or lost sync).</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Used in <ref refid="structbt__le__per__adv__sync__cb" kindref="compound">bt_le_per_adv_sync_cb</ref> structure. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
